fr.faylixe.googlecodejam.client

Class CodeJamSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.faylixe.googlecodejam.client.common.NamedObject
      • fr.faylixe.googlecodejam.client.CodeJamSession
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class CodeJamSession
extends NamedObject
implements Serializable

    CodeJamSession is the main API entry point, which consists in logging to a code jam platform hostname and then providing facilities such as :


    • Retrieves contest, round
    • Interacts with platform API from a given round
    • Downloads input
    • Submits solutions
    Author:
    fv

      • submit

        public SubmitResponse submit(ProblemInput input,
                             File output,
                             File source)
                      throws IOException
        Submits the given output file and the given source file for the given problem input. This method should be call only after a successful call to the download(ProblemInput) method on the same input, as the evaluation system will judge the last downloaded dataset based on the internal token / session.
        Parameters:
        input - Input file to submit solution for.
        output - Output file produced by the algorithm.
        source - Source code file of the algorithm to submit.
        Returns:
        Request response, as a SubmitResponse instance.
        Throws:
        IOException - If any error occurs while uploading data, or performing the request.

      • createSession

        public static CodeJamSession createSession(HttpRequestExecutor executor,
                                           Round round)
                                    throws IOException
        Static factory method that should be used for creating a session. Loads associated contest info and initial values from the given round, using the given executor.
        Parameters:
        executor - HttpRequestExecutor instance to use.
        round - Contextual Round instance this session is bound to.
        Returns:
        Created session.
        Throws:
        IOException - If any error occurs while retrieving contest info or initial values.
